HEADWORD: Old World
<hw>Old World</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The combined territories of
Europe, Asia, and Africa. The Eastern Hemisphere, as distinguished from
The Americas, Australia, and the Pacific Islands.</def>⟦br⟧
